Note 
There is an setup hold critical path in PT 
Setup violated scenario : both_all_ss0p675v0c_cworst_T_0
Same path hold Scenario: hold_all_ff0p825v0c_cbest_0
Where setup is violated by -30ps and we have hold margin +40ps
For this case its very hard to fix the setup because for setup fixing swapping and upsize has to be done but it degrades the hold as well because we don’t have enough hold margin .
While am observing the comb cells of the path the tool added delay buffers to fix the hold (HDB54SVT03_DEL_R2V1_1 ) and setup violated 
Because the delay offered by the delay cell in hold corner is 19 ps but in setup corner it offered  49ps 

In general for hold fixing we need huge delay for a cell in hold scenario so we will be using low drive strength cells and lower VT cells like SVT, LVTLL 

In this case the VT cells used to fix hold offers less delay in hold and huge delay in setup 
So I have swapped SVT to ULT to fix the violation so therby I gained +25 ps in setup side for same cell where in hold side it degraded by 7 ps because of ult swapping the next delay buffer delay reduced by 5ps there by now setup of this path is fixed by without degrading hold 
   
